## Pitfall check promoted to agent tool (check_owl_pitfalls)

### Context
Previously the pitfall loop was external to the agent: Python code ran the check
after each OWL text response, then injected synthetic user messages to trigger a
fix. The user requested making this a proper tool the agent calls itself, so the
agent owns the validate → fix → re-validate cycle.

### Changes
1. **NEW `src/agents/tools/pitfalls.py`**
   - `tool_check_owl_pitfalls(ctx, *, turtle_text)` — parses Turtle, runs
     `PitfallsService`, returns JSON: `{score, is_clean, total_warnings,
     warnings:[{id,title,count,items,hint}], fix_instruction}`.
   - Moved `NON_ML_PATTERNS`, `PATTERN_FIX_HINTS`, `_item_label` here from engine.py.
   - `PITFALL_TOOL_DEFINITIONS` / `PITFALL_TOOL_HANDLERS` — function-calling schema.

2. `src/agents/agent_owl_generator/tools.py`
   - Imported and wired in `PITFALL_TOOL_DEFINITIONS` + `PITFALL_TOOL_HANDLERS`.

3. `src/agents/agent_owl_generator/engine.py`
   - Updated `SYSTEM_PROMPT` `# TOOLS` and `# WORKFLOW` sections: agent now has five
     tools; step 5 instructs it to ALWAYS call `check_owl_pitfalls` and loop until
     `is_clean=true`, step 6 to output final Turtle only when clean.
   - Removed `_PitfallRound`, `_check_owl_pitfalls`, `_PATTERN_FIX_HINTS`,
     `_NON_ML_PATTERNS`, `_item_label` — all moved to the tool module.
   - Replaced the external post-text-response pitfall loop with in-loop detection:
     when `tool_name == "check_owl_pitfalls"` is dispatched, parse result, emit
     `__iter__` event, update `iteration_summary`, and enforce `max_fix_rounds` cap
     by disabling tools (forcing final output) when budget is exhausted.
   - Removed unused `score_threshold` / `stop_on_no_critical` config variables.
   - Simplified `else` branch to unconditionally accept the text response as
     final OWL (the agent has already validated via the tool).

### Modified files
- src/agents/tools/pitfalls.py (new)
- src/agents/agent_owl_generator/tools.py
- src/agents/agent_owl_generator/engine.py

### Test result
2302 passed, 15 skipped — all green

